data.title: Concordia University Wisconsin
data.meta_description: Concordia University Wisconsin is a 4-year, NCA-accredited, co-educational, liberal arts school offering undergraduate, graduate, adult accelerated, online, and international programs.
data.text:
Mequon Adjunct Faculty In-Service (In-Person Classes)

Event Date: Tuesday, Aug. 20, 2024

The fall semester begins August 26! During this session for adjuncts teaching in-person classes on the Mequon campus, we will share important changes for this semester.

Mequon Campus

Experience it for yourself

CUW is famous for our beautiful campus on 200 acres of lakefront property on the shores of Lake Michigan. We are located in Mequon, Wisconsin, which is about 20 minutes North of Milwaukee.
